question.title: ZipException while opening "jna-4.0.0.jar": Invalid CEN header (invalid zip64 extra data field size) Error. When running project with maven command
question.body:
When Ä± run my test automation with "maven clean install" command, I get an error:

[ERROR] COMPILATION ERROR : 
[INFO] -------------------------------------------------------------
[ERROR] error reading /Users/public/.m2/repository/net/java/dev/jna/jna/4.0.0/jna-4.0.0.jar; Invalid CEN header (invalid zip64 extra data field size)

I encountered no problems when I downloaded and ran the same project on a different computer. I deleted the C:/Users/public/.m2/repository file and ran it again, but it gave the same error.

is it an IDE-related problem? If not, what is the source of it.
